00:32:07.810 --> 00:32:10.546
And maybe the truth is

731
00:32:10.546 --> 00:32:12.915
like a baby growing in the womb,

732
00:32:12.915 --> 00:32:16.251
we are self-centered, self-conscious species.

733
00:32:16.251 --> 00:32:18.521
We probably have many faults and we don't know

734
00:32:18.521 --> 00:32:21.191
'til we see another planet go through this,

