00:32:21.191 --> 00:32:22.925
but the most dangerous time

736
00:32:22.925 --> 00:32:25.761
for any intelligent species is when you hit

737
00:32:25.761 --> 00:32:28.898
your high-tech, over-populating, polluting phase

738
00:32:28.898 --> 00:32:31.000
with this degree of power,

739
00:32:31.000 --> 00:32:35.838
that came from our intelligence, to survive.

